      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? I'm parting with this absolute beauty, and honestly, it\u2019s in incredible shape. It\u2019s been kept in a garage, meticulously cared for, and drives like a total dream. You won\u2019t find a single scratch or hiccup here\u2014it\u2019s basically brand new! I\u2019m looking for someone who will love it as much as I have. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 43500.0,
